---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Contacto | Solicita Tu Presupuesto" description="Contáctanos para una consulta gratuita." activePage="contacto">
  <header class="page-hero"><div class="hero-bg" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600607687920-4e2a09cf159d?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop')"></div><div class="hero-overlay"></div><div class="hero-content"><span class="hero-tag">Contáctanos</span><h1 class="page-title">Hablemos de <span class="gold">Tu Proyecto</span></h1><p class="page-subtitle">Estamos aquí para escucharte, asesorarte y hacer realidad la transformación.</p></div></header>
  <section class="contact-page"><div class="container"><div class="contact-grid"><div class="contact-info"><h2 class="section-title">Información de Contacto</h2><p class="contact-desc">Completa el formulario. Respondemos en menos de 24 horas.</p><div class="contact-item"><div class="contact-icon">📍</div><div><h4>Ubicación</h4><p>Valencia y San Diego, Carabobo</p></div></div><div class="contact-item"><div class="contact-icon">📞</div><div><h4>Teléfono</h4><p>0422 799 7043</p></div></div><div class="contact-item"><div class="contact-icon">✉️</div><div><h4>Email</h4><p>hola@reformatvenezuela.online</p></div></div><div class="contact-item"><div class="contact-icon">⏰</div><div><h4>Horario</h4><p>Lun - Vie: 8:00 AM - 6:00 PM<br/>Sáb: 9:00 AM - 1:00 PM</p></div></div><div class="social-links"><a href="#" class="social-btn">Instagram</a><a href="https://wa.me/584227997043" class="social-btn">WhatsApp</a></div></div><form class="contact-form" id="contactForm"><h3>Solicita Tu Presupuesto Gratuito</h3><div class="form-row"><div class="form-group"><label>Nombre</label><input type="text" required placeholder="Tu nombre" /></div><div class="form-group"><label>Apellido</label><input type="text" required placeholder="Tu apellido" /></div></div><div class="form-row"><div class="form-group"><label>Email</label><input type="email" required placeholder="tu@email.com" /></div><div class="form-group"><label>Teléfono</label><input type="tel" required placeholder="04XX XXX XXXX" /></div></div><div class="form-group"><label>Tipo de Proyecto</label><select required><option value="" disabled selected>Selecciona una opción</option><option value="cocina">Reforma de Cocina</option><option value="bano">Reforma de Baño</option><option value="integral">Reforma Integral</option><option value="otro">Otro</option></select></div><div class="form-group"><label>Tu Mensaje</label><textarea rows="5" placeholder="Cuéntanos sobre tu proyecto..."></textarea></div><button type="submit" class="btn-premium btn-primary-premium"><span class="btn-content">Enviar Mensaje</span><span class="btn-border"></span><span class="btn-shine"></span><span class="btn-arrow">→</span></button></form></div></div></section>
  
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="cta-wrapper">
      <h2 class="cta-title">¿Listo Para Empezar?</h2>
      <p class="cta-text">Tu transformación comienza con un simple mensaje.</p>
      <a href="/contacto" class="btn-premium btn-primary-premium"><span class="btn-content">Contactar Ahora</span><span class="btn-border"></span><span class="btn-shine"></span><span class="btn-arrow">→</span></a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
<style>
  .contact-page { padding: 100px 0; background: var(--gray); }
  .contact-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr; gap: 60px; }
  .contact-desc { color: var(--gray-text); margin-bottom: 40px; line-height: 1.8; }
  .contact-item { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
  .contact-icon { width: 50px; height: 50px; background: var(--bg); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.3rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .contact-item h4 { font-size: 0.9rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 5px; }
  .contact-item p { color: var(--gray-text); font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .social-links { display: flex; gap: 15px; margin-top: 40px; }
  .social-btn { padding: 10px 20px; background: var(--bg); color: var(--white); border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.85rem; text-decoration: none; transition: 0.3s; }
  .social-btn:hover { background: var(--gold); color: var(--bg); }
  .contact-form { background: var(--white); padding: 50px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
  .contact-form h3 { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 30px; }
  .form-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; }
  .form-group { margin-bottom: 25px; }
  .form-group label { display: block; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .form-group input, .form-group select, .form-group textarea { width: 100%; padding: 14px; border: 1px solid #ddd; background: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 4px; font-family: inherit; }
  .form-group input:focus, .form-group textarea:focus, .form-group select:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--gold); background: var(--white); }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
<script>
  const form = document.getElementById('contactForm'); if(form) form.addEventListener('submit', e => { e.preventDefault(); const btn = form.querySelector('.btn-premium'); const original = btn.querySelector('.btn-content').textContent; btn.querySelector('.btn-content').textContent = '✓ Enviado'; btn.style.background = '#4a7c59'; setTimeout(() => { btn.querySelector('.btn-content').textContent = original; btn.style.background = ''; form.reset(); }, 3000); });
</script>